# Session 18 Handover — Fumage

## What was done this session

### Two new fragrances added to catalog

Both fragrances were researched from Fragrantica, Parfumo, official brand sites, Basenotes, and community consensus, then added to `prisma/data/fragrance_database.json` and seeded into the live database. Commit `80803f7`.

**Terre d'Hermès Eau Givrée** — slug `herm-s-terre-d-herm-s-eau-givr-e`
- EDP, 2022, Christine Nagel
- Family: Citrus / Citrus Woody
- Notes: Cedrat → Juniper Berry, Timur Pepper → Woody Notes, Mineral Notes
- Performance: longevity 7 / projection 6 / sillage 6
- Seasons: spring, summer, fall | Occasions: casual, business, date | Day
- Price: $137–$175 (MID) | Rating: 4.2/5 | Popularity: 70
- Trend: Rising | Hype: Underrated | Mass appeal: Yes | Compliment: High
- Award: 2023 Fragrance Foundation USA Men's Prestige Fragrance of the Year

**Le Sel d'Issey** — slug `issey-miyake-le-sel-d-issey`
- EDT, 2024, Quentin Bisch (Givaudan)
- Family: Fresh / Fresh Marine Woody
- Notes: Salt, Ginger → Seaweed, Vetiver, Oakmoss → Cedarwood, Akigalawood
- Performance: longevity 7 / projection 6 / sillage 6
- Seasons: spring, summer, fall | Occasions: casual, business, date | Day
- Price: $85–$139 (MID) | Rating: 3.9/5 | Popularity: 55
- Trend: Rising | Hype: Underrated | Mass appeal: No | Compliment: Moderate
- Award: 2025 Fragrantica Best Masculine Award (EDT)
- First Issey Miyake refillable men's fragrance

